        <name>DT_MEMORY_ATTR_FOREACH_STATUS_OKAY_NODE</name>
        <param><defname>fn</defname></param>
        <initializer>	<ref refid="group__devicetree-generic-foreach_1ga9aa3ee2b90a4ec30621597f4d1448c51" kindref="member">DT_FOREACH_STATUS_OKAY_NODE_VARGS</ref>(_FILTER, fn)</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Invokes <computeroutput>fn</computeroutput> for every status <computeroutput>okay</computeroutput> node in the tree with property <computeroutput>zephyr,memory-attr</computeroutput> </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The macro <computeroutput>fn</computeroutput> must take one parameter, which will be a node identifier with the <computeroutput>zephyr,memory-attr</computeroutput> property. The macro is expanded once for each node in the tree with status <computeroutput>okay</computeroutput>. The order that nodes are visited in is not specified.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>fn</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>macro to invoke </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
